Package parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractParser
    Abstract class that declares common methods and instance variables for each file type parser.
    DirectoryParser
    Recursively takes all input files in directory and parses them according to file type.
    FileParser
    Takes input file and parses according to file type.
    ParseCephData
    Standardizes .gateway and .keyring files (auto-generated by ceph)
    ParseConf
    Standardizes .config files.
    ParseHosts
    Standardizes hosts files.
    ParseIgnore
    Standardizes hosts files.
    ParseInfo
    Standardizes .info files.
    ParseList
    Standardizes .whitelist and .blacklist files
    ParseProp
    Standardizes .property files.
    ParseXML
    Standardizes hazelcast.xml files and cluster.xml files.
    ParseYaml
    Standardizes .yaml files.
